sections.heading: Livestock, defined.Livestock means any domestic cattle, horses, mules, donkeys, sheep, or swine
sections.text: SourceLaws 1999, LB 778, ยง 14.AnnotationsDogs are not livestock and the care or production of dogs cannot be included in the term animal husbandry. City of Beatrice v. Goodenkauf, 219 Neb. 756, 366 N.W.2d
